Let’s talk business

What we do

   VirtualExpo Group is a world leader in the online B2B lead generation
   market. We give businesses and buyers of all sizes access to a million
   specific products in one place. Thanks to our performant SEO tools and
   specialized sites in 9 languages, we continue to attract millions of
   online buyers, manufacturers, and distributors.

We’re everywhere

Our specializations

   We are specialized in six sectors with our six B2B websites.

     *
   AeroExpo
       AeroExpo

AERONAUTICS
       AeroExpo is a leading sourcing tool for buyers, production
       managers, maintenance managers and consulting engineers in the
       aeronautic field.
          + 2.5K+ Exhibitors/year
          + 35.3K+ Products
          + 100K Visitors/month
       DISCOVER
     *
   AgriExpo
       AgriExpo

AGRICULTURE
       AgriExpo is a leading sourcing tool for crop and livestock farmers,
       traders, cooperatives and other professionals in the agricultural
       and forestry fields.
          + 3K+ Exhibitors/year
          + 65.6K+ Products
          + 250K Visitors/month
       DISCOVER
     *
   ArchiExpo
       ArchiExpo

ARCHITECTURE AND DESIGN
       ArchiExpo is a leading sourcing tool for architects, interior
       designers, and construction companies.
          + 10.2K+ Exhibitors/year
          + 449K+ Products
          + 2M Visitors/month
       DISCOVER
     *
   DirectIndustry
       DirectIndustry

INDUSTRY
       DirectIndustry is a leading sourcing tool for buyers, production
       managers, maintenance managers and consulting engineers.
          + 13K+ Exhibitors/year
          + 472K+ Products
          + 2.4M Visitors/month
       DISCOVER
     *
   MedicalExpo
       MedicalExpo

MEDICINE AND TECHNOLOGY
