We’re multi-talented

Other Businesses

   Our additional services help you to get an even better experience with
   us complimented with a competitive advantage in your B2B sector.

     *

VirtualStore
       VirtualStore gives more visibility to our distributor partners and
       helps them grow their business on the web. To accomplish this, we
       propose a set of services ranging from lead generation to
       a complete solution and a turnkey website. Our network of reseller
       partners helps us to better meet the expectations of our buyers.
       Interested? Contact us
     *

e-Magazine
       We have three e-magazines that reach 263,000 international
       subscribers of professionals and enthusiasts in each field. Our
       e-magazines are a creative space run by professional journalists
       that cover news and trends in different industries. Therefore, they
       offer an opportunity for targeted advertising as well as helping
       our clients reach a bigger audience and expand their image in a
       different way.
       Discover more

we know our audiences

Our B2B Audiences

   We proudly target an international audience of buyers, manufacturers,
   and distributors through our six B2B platforms.

     *
   Buyers

Buyers
       We give buyers a complete B2B product hunting experience so they
       can easily find quality products from top manufacturers in six
       different sectors. Buyers can stay updated on industry news and
       trends; locate nearest points of sale; request and compare custom
       price quotes and documentation from leading manufacturers; and
       browse thousands of products worldwide.
       Learn More
     *
   Manufacturers

Manufacturers
       With each of our websites, manufacturers benefit from our
       customized services and specialized SEO tools that allow them to
       increase their online visibility and bring traffic to their
       websites. Manufacturers can reach their business goals by
       exhibiting their products with us to achieve sales leads,
       international visibility, brand building, sales networks, and
       measurable results.
       Learn More
     *
   Distributors

Distributors
       We offer distributors the tools to receive sales leads as well as
       the possibility to create a VirtualStore— a website hosting service
       and reseller network to reach more online visibility and lead
       generation.
       Distributors are also displayed on our “Where to Buy” map featured
       on our websites where serious potential buyers can easily locate
       their closest points of sale.
       Learn More

